OL,4,CUnpaid carers being forced to repay
OL,5,C#250m to DWP
OL,6,GUnpaid carers must repay more than
OL,7,G#250 million after many were
OL,8,Gunknowingly overpaid their allowance,
OL,9,Gnew figures show.
OL,11,FThe government is seeking to recover
OL,12,Fmoney from more than 134,000 carers.
OL,14,FCarer's Allowance must be repaid in
OL,15,Ffull if a strict earnings limit is
OL,16,Fexceeded by even a few pence.
OL,18,FThe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,19,F(DWP) said it was "progressing an
OL,20,Fenhanced notification strategy" to
OL,21,Falert carers to overpayments.
